cs.LG, cs.NE, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.SD

This paper is likely to belong to the sub-category of cs.LG (Machine Learning) as it presents a method for storing multiple models within a single set of parameters and experiments with neural networks. It could also belong to cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) as it deals with neural networks. Additionally, it could be categorized under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) as it presents a novel approach to utilizing the capacity of a network during training. The paper also mentions experiments with image classification, which could place it under cs.CV (Computer Vision). Finally, the paper could be categorized under cs.SD (Software Development) as it presents a new approach to model storage and retrieval.
